                    "ability_type": "offensive",
                    "frequency": "once per day, plus overcharge",
                    "effect": "You cast *impending doom* of the indicated rank, showing the target a potential death that's gruesome and absurd. If the target becomes frightened by the spell, it also becomes stupefied with a value 1 higher than the frightened value. This lasts for the duration of the spell.",
